Package: AlphaVaR
Title: Analysis and Visualization of AlphaGenome Variant Effect Scores
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Karim", "Marhaba", , "ka.marhaba@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Transforms raw CSV outputs from AlphaGenome into biological insights. 
    Includes annotation, statistical enrichment calculation, quality control, 
    and report generation.
